20it%20just%20a%20bad%20day%20or%20something%20deeper%20than%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20propose%20that%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20were%20afflicted%20by%20a%20pervasive%2C%20oppressive%20sense%20of%20neediness.%20We%20are%20a%20needy%20people.%20We%20need.%20Even%20when%20we%20have%20plenty.%20We%20may%20be%20teaching%20the%20world%20the%20principle%20of%20'simple%20living%2C%20high%20thinking'%20but%20we%20are%20a%20desperately%20needy%20lot.%20And%20what%20we%20need%20the%20most%20is%20validation.%20Our%20sense%20of%20being%20needs%20to%20be%20reassured%20all%20the%20time.%20We%20can't%20savour%20victory%20without%20reassurances%20about%20our%20greatness.%20We%20are%20always%20out%20there%20to%20prove%20a%20point.%20Even%20after%20we%20have%20made%20that%20point.%20We%20are%20never%20sure%20of%20our%20most%20tangible%20achievements.%20It's%20as%20if%20our%20achievements%20and%20glories%20are%20tenuous%20as%20tendrils%20that%20even%20the%20mildest%20draft%20threatens%20to%20shake%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fmpfadjeg_virat-kohli-siraj-afp_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20our%20unseemly%20bellies%2C%20but%20even%20our%20psychological%20make-up%20seems%20to%20be%20still%20defined%20by%20our%20ancestral%20feast-and-famine%20cycles.%20Even%20while%20feasting%2C%20we%20cannot%20savour%20anything%20because%20we%20are%20scared%20of%20being%20famished%20the%20next%20moment.%20We%20are%20also%20prickly%20about%20being%20reminded%20of%20our%20famished%20days.%20We%20are%20nervous.%20What%20kind%20of%20civilisational%20superiority%20can%20we%20claim%20if%20our%20insecurity%20overshadows%20our%20feats%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australians%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20brought%20the%20ease%20of%20Bondi%20Beach%20t