0India%20would%20have%20won.%20Now%20it%20can%20be%20heard%20that%20there%20was%20some%20issue%20with%20the%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20here%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20bundled%20out%20on%20a%20score%20of%20240%20in%2050%20overs.%20On%20a%20tough%20batting%20surface%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(47%20in%2031%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20(54%20in%2063%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries)%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20(66%20in%20107%20balls%2C%20with%20one%20four)%20posted%20important%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitchell%20Starc%20(3%2F55)%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20Australia.%20Skipper%20Pat%20Cummins%20(2%2F34)%20and%20Josh%20Hazlewood%20(2%2F60)%20also%20bowled%20well.%20Adam%20Zampa%20and%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20got%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20chasing%20241%2C%20India%20had%20the%20Aussies%20down%20at%2047%2F3.%20Knocks%20from%20Travis%20Head%20(137%20in%20120%20balls%2C%20with%2015%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Marnus%20Labuschagne%20(58%20in%20110%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries)%20left%20the%20Indian%20team%20without%20answers%2C%20and%20Australia%20won%20by%20six%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20finalists%20will%20now%20compete%20in%20a%20five-match%20T20I%20series%20which%20will%20begin%20from%20November%2023%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700627340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fjnm0a9qo_akhilesh-yadav-ndtv-conclave-650_625x300_17_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-says-india-would-have-won-world-cup-if-it-had-happen-in-lucknow-4594682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samajwadi%