ps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5qqjSjvt4X%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5qqjSjvt4X%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20%E2%80%93%20Qatar%20(%40MofaQatar_EN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMofaQatar_EN%2Fstatus%2F1727170260154151248%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHamas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20Hamas%20has%20released%20an%20official%20statement%20that%20recognises%20the%20following%20terms%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20A%20ceasefire%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20a%20cessation%20of%20all%20military%20actions%20by%20occupation%20forces%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20and%20a%20cessation%20of%20the%20movement%20of%20its%20military%20vehicles%20penetrating%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20entry%20of%20hundreds%20of%20trucks%20of%20humanitarian%2C%20relief%2C%20medical%20and%20fuel%20aid%20into%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20without%20exception%2C%20in%20the%20north%20and%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20release%20of%2050%20women%20and%20children%20of%20the%20occupation%E2%80%99s%20detainees%2C%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20years%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20release%20of%20150%20women%20and%20children%20of%20our%20people%20from%20the%20occupation%E2%80%99s%20prisons%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20years%2C%20in%20order%20of%20time%20imprisoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Stopping%20all%20occupation%20air%20traffic%20in%20the%20south%20for%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Stopping%20all%20occupation%20air%20traffic%20in%20the%20North%20for%206%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20from%2010%3A00%20AM%20until%204%3A00%20PM.%20During%20the%20truce%20period%2C%20the%20occupation%20is%20committed%20not%20to%20attack%20or%20arrest%20anyone%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C