Hostages%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Hamas%20militants%20took%20hostages%20during%20their%20deadly%20assault%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Qatar%20contacted%20the%20White%20House%20with%20a%20request%3A%20Form%20a%20small%20team%20of%20advisers%20to%20help%20work%20to%20get%20the%20captives%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20work%2C%20begun%20in%20the%20days%20after%20the%20hostages%20were%20taken%2C%20finally%20bore%20fruit%20with%20the%20announcement%20of%20a%20prisoner%20swap%20deal%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20and%20agreed%20by%20Israel%2C%20Hamas%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20secretive%20effort%20included%20tense%20personal%20diplomatic%20engagement%20by%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20held%20a%20number%20of%20urgent%20conversations%20with%20emir%20of%20Qatar%20and%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20involved%20hours%20of%20painstaking%20negotiations%20including%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20CIA%20Director%20Bill%20Burns%2C%20national%20security%20adviser%20Jake%20Sullivan%20and%20his%20deputy%20Jon%20Finer%2C%20and%20U.S.%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20Brett%20McGurk%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20officials%20involved%20in%20the%20effort%20provided%20extensive%20details%20of%20the%20work%20that%20led%20to%20an%20agreement%20in%20which%2050%20hostages%20are%20to%20be%20freed%20in%20exchange%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20during%20a%20four-day%20pause%20in%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Oct.%207%2C%20Qatar%20-%20a%20long-established%20mediator%20in%20a%20volatile%20region%20-%20approached%20the%20White%20House%20with%20sensitive%20information%20regarding%20the%20hostages%20and%20the%20potential%20for%20their%20release%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20The%20Qataris%20asked%20that%20a%20small%20team%2C%20which%20they%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bcell%2C%26quot%3B%20be%20established%20to%20work%20the%20issue%20privately%20with%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESullivan%20directed%20McGurk%20and%20another%20National%20Security%20Council%20official%2C%20Josh%20Geltzer%2C%20to%20establish%20the%20team.%20This%20was%20done%20without%20telling%20other%20relevant%20U.S.%20agencies%20because%20Qatar%20and%20Israel%20demanded%20extreme%20secrecy%20with%20only%20a%20few%20people%20to%20be%20in%20the%20know%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcGurk%2C%20a%20seasoned%20diplomat%20with%20deep%20experience%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20held%20daily%20morning%20calls%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Mohammed%20bin%20Abdulrahman%20bin%20Jassim%20Al%20Thani.%20He%20reported%20back%20to%20Sullivan%20and%20Biden%20was%20briefed%20daily%20on%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20got%20an%20upfront%20look%20at%20what%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20endured%20when%20he%20held%20an%20emotional%2C%20lengthy%20meeting%20on%20Oct.%2013%20with%20the%20families%20of%20Americans%20who%20were%20either%20being%20held%20hostage%20or%20were%20unaccounted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20Biden%20traveled%20to%20Tel%20Aviv%20for%20Oct.%2018%20talks%20with%20Netanyahu.%20The%20official%20said%20securing%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20was%20a%20central%20focus%20of%20his%20discussions%20with%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20war%20cabinet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20humanitarian%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20on%20Oct.%2023%2C%20the%20White%20House%20team's%20work%20helped%20yield%20the%20release%20of%20two%20American%20hostages%2C%20Natalie%20and%20Judith%20Raanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20outside%20Sullivan's%20West%20Wing%20office%20McGurk%2C%20Sullivan%20and%20Finer%20tracked%20in%20real%20time%20the%20captives'%20difficult%2C%20multi-hour%20journey%20out%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20the%20two%20Americans%20proved%20it%20was%20possible%20to%20gain%20freedom%20for%20hostages%20and%20gave%20confidence%20to%20Biden%20that%20Qatar%20could%20deliver%20through%20the%20small%20team%20that%20had%20been%20established%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20an%20intensified%20process%20started%20to%20get%20more%20hostages%20out.%20When%20this%20happened%2C%20Burns%20began%20speaking%20regularly%20with%20Mossad%20director%20David%20Barnea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20gain%20the%20release%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20hostages%20and%20that%20a%20deal%20for%20prisoners%20was%20the%20only%20realistic%20path%20to%20securing%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Oct.%2024%2C%20with%20Israel%20poised%20to%20launch%20a%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20U.S.%20side%20got%20word%20that%20Hamas%20had%20agreed%20to%20the%20parameters%20of%20a%20deal%20to%20release%20women%20and%20children%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20a%20pause%20and%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20officials%20debated%20with%20the%20Israelis%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20ground%20offensive%20should%20be%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israelis%20argued%20that%20terms%20were%20not%20firm%20enough%20to%20delay%2C%20since%20there%20was%20no%20proof%20of%20life%20for%20the%20hostages.%20Hamas%20claimed%20they%20could%20not%20determine%20who%20was%20being%20held%20until%20a%20pause%20in%20fighting%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20and%20Israelis%20viewed%20the%20Hamas%20position%20as%20disingenuous.%20The%20official%20said%20Israel's%20invasion%20plan%20was%20adapted%20to%20support%20a%20pause%20if%20a%20deal%20came%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20then%20engaged%20over%20the%20next%20three%20weeks%20in%20detailed%20talks%20as%20proposals%20about%20a%20potential%20hostage%20release%20were%20traded%20back%20and%20forth.%20Demands%20were%20made%20that%20Hamas%20produce%20the%20lists%20of%20hostages%20it%20was%20holding%2C%20their%20identifying%20information%2C%20and%20guarantees%20of%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20long%20and%20cumbersome%20-%20communication%20was%20difficult%20and%20messages%20had%20to%20be%20passed%20from%20Doha%20or%20Cairo%20into%20Gaza%20and%20back%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20held%20a%20previously%20undisclosed%20phone%20call%20with%20the%20Qatari%20prime%20minister%20when%20the%20phasing%20of%20releases%20began%20to%20take%20shape%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20agreement%20that%20was%20taking%20shape%2C%20women%20and%20children%20hostages%20would%20be%20freed%20in%20a%20first%20phase%2C%20together%20with%20a%20commensurate%20release%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20from%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20The%20Israelis%20insisted%20Hamas%20ensure%20all%20women%20and%20children%20come%20out%20in%20this%20phase.%20The%20U.S.%20side%20agreed%2C%20and%20demanded%20through%20Qatar%20proof%20of%20life%20or%20identifying%20information%20for%20women%20and%20children%20held%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20it%20could%20guarantee%2050%20in%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20produce%20a%20list%20of%20identifying%20criteria.%20On%20November%209%2C%20Burns%20met%20in%20Doha%20with%20the%20Qatari%20leader%20and%20the%20Mossad's%20Barnea%20to%20go%20through%20the%20texts%20of%20the%20emerging%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20obstacle%20at%20that%20point%20was%20that%20Hamas%20had%20not%20clearly%20identified%20who%20it%20was%20holding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20Biden%20called%20the%20emir%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamad%20Al%20Thani%2C%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20the%20names%20or%20clear%20identifying%20information%20for%20the%2050%20hostages%20including%20ages%2C%20gender%20and%20nationalities.%20Without%20the%20information%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20there%20was%20no%20basis%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20Biden's%20call%2C%20Hamas%20produced%20details%20for%20the%2050%20hostages%20it%20said%20would%20be%20released%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20any%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20in%20a%20Nov.%2014%20call%20urged%20Netanyahu%20to%20take%20the%20deal%20-%20Netanyahu%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcGurk%20saw%20Netanyahu%20that%20same%20day%20in%20Israel.%20Walking%20out%20of%20a%20meeting%2C%20Netanyahu%20grabbed%20McGurk's%20arm%20and%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20this%20deal%E2%80%9D%20and%20urged%20Biden%20call%20the%20emir%20of%20Qatar%20on%20the%20final%20terms%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20stalled%20as%20communications%20went%20dark%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20resumed%2C%20Biden%20was%20in%20San%20Francisco%20attending%20an%20Asia-Pacific%20summit.%20He%20called%20the%20emir%20of%20Qatar%20and%20told%20him%20this%20was%20the%20last%20chance%2C%20and%20the%20emir%20pledged%20to%20apply%20pressure%20to%20close%20the%20deal%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20president%20insisted%20the%20deal%20had%20to%20close%2C%20now.%20Time%20was%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Nov.%2018%2C%20McGurk%20met%20in%20Doha%20with%20the%20Qatari%20prime%20minister.%20Burns%20was%20dialed%20in%20after%20he%20spoke%20with%20Mossad.%20The%20meeting%20identified%20the%20last%20remaining%20gaps%20toward%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20was%20now%20structured%20for%20women%20and%20children%20to%20be%20freed%20in%20the%20first%20phase%2C%20but%20with%20an%20expectation%20for%20future%20releases%20and%20the%20aim%20to%20bring%20all%20hostages%20home%20to%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Cairo%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20McGurk%20met%20with%20Egypt%20intelligence%20chief%20Abbas%20Kamil.%20Word%20came%20from%20Hamas%20leaders%20in%20Gaza%20that%20they%20had%20accepted%20nearly%20all%20the%20agreements%20worked%20out%20the%20day%20before%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20one%20issue%20remained%2C%20tied%20to%20the%20number%20of%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20and%20the%20ultimate%20structure%20of%20the%20deal%20to%20incentivize%20releases%20beyond%20the%2050%20known%20women%20and%20children%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%20A%20flurry%20of%20additional%20contacts%20ensued%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20finally%20came%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700626320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2qvc7lr8_biden-qatar_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-deal-explainer-secret-negotiations-that-led-to-israel-hamas-hostages-deal-4594975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20Hamas%20militants%20took%20hostages%20during%20their%20deadly%20assault%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Qatar%20contacted%20the%20White%20House%20with%20a%20request%3A%20Form%20a%20small%20team%20of%20advisers%20to%20help%20work%20to%20get%20the%20captives%20freed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-deal-explainer-secret-negotiations-that-led-to-israel-hamas-hostages-deal-4594975%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-deal-explainer-secret-negotiations-that-led-to-israel-hamas-hostages-deal-4594975%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-deal-explainer-secret-negotiations-that-led-to-israel-hamas-hostages-deal-4594975%2Famp