ren%2527t%2520safe%2Con%2520Instagram%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520he%2520ignored%2520me%2527%26amp%3Btext%3DInstagram%252Downer%2520Meta%2520is%2520%25E2%2580%259Cfundamentally%2C%252Dturned%252Dwhistleblower%2520has%2520said.%5C%22%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20overall%20design%20of%20Instagram%20is%20not%20conducive%20to%20encouraging%20teenagers%20to%20report%20things%20that%20make%20them%20uncomfortable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bejar%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20technology%20industry%20since%20he%20was%2015%2C%20joined%20the%20company%20then%20known%20as%20Facebook%20in%202009.%20He%20joined%20as%20an%20engineering%20director%20in%20the%20company's%20Protect%20and%20Care%20team.%20He%20left%20in%202015%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20his%20children.%20However%2C%20by%202019%2C%20he%20had%20grown%20concerned%20that%20his%20daughter%2C%20who%20was%2014%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20receiving%20unwanted%20sexual%20advances%20on%20Instagram.%20So%20he%20returned%20to%20Meta%20as%20a%20consultant%20to%20work%20on%20safety%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bejar's%20second%20stint%20at%20the%20company%20coincided%20with%20a%20series%20of%20damaging%20leaks%20about%20Meta.%20In%202021%2C%20data%20scientist%20Frances%20Haugen%20went%20public%20and%20handed%20a%20dossier%20of%20information%20to%20US%20senators.%20Her%20claim%20was%20research%20that%20appeared%20to%20show%20Meta%20knew%20Instagram%20was%20making%20teenage%20girls%20feel%20worse%20about%20themselves.%20But%20the%20company%20strongly%20denied%20these%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ms%20Haugen%20was%20going%20public%2C%20Mr%20Bejar%20said%20that%20he%20was%20pushing%20privately%20for%20a%20change.%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20flagged%20his%20concern%20to%20Sheryl%20Sandberg%2C%20Facebook's%20operations%20chief%2C%20and%20Instagram%20lead%20Adam%20Mosseri.%20He%20reportedly%20also%20sent%20a%20private%20mail%20to%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20with%20detailed%20research%20about%20how%20teenagers%20were%20experiencing%20more%20harm%20on%20Instagram%20than%20previously%20thought.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Bejar%20said%20that%20his%20concerns%20were%20brushed%20off%20and%20Mr%20Zuckerberg%20never%20replied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20them%20ignoring%20what%20can%20be%20described%20as%20statistically%20significant%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20suggested%20millions%20of%20teenagers%20were%20experiencing%20safety%20issues%20while%20using%20Meta's%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-knew-about-tesla-autopilot-glitch-still-let-cars-run-says-us-judge-4594763%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20Knew%20About%20Tesla%20Autopilot%20Glitch%2C%20Still%20Let%20Cars%20Run%2C%20Says%20US%20Judge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20discloses%20figures%20on%20incidents%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%20bullying%20and%20harassment%20on%20its%20social%20networks%20as%20part%20of%20regular%20transparency%20reports.%20However%2C%20Mr%20Bejar%20argued%20that%20the%20numbers%20are%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20and%20misrepresenting%26quot%3B%20the%20problem%20as%20they%20disclose%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bfraction%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20true%20harm.%20He%20claimed%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20negative%20experiences%20on%20Instagram%20do%20not%20break%20its%20rules%20and%20even%20when%20content%20does%20break%20the%20rules%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20speaking%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20to%20suggest%26quot%3B%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bsome%20sort%20of%20conflict%26quot%3B%20between%20its%20study%20of%20users'%20%26quot%3Bperception%26quot%3B%20of%20Instagram%20and%20its%20transparency%20reports.%20%26quot%3BPrevalence%20metrics%20and%20user%20perception%20surveys%20measure%20two%20different%20things.%20We%20take%20actions%20based%20on%20both%20and%20work%20on%20both%20continues%20to%20this%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Bejar%20stated%20social%20media%20companies%20should%20be%20compelled%20to%20better%20collect%20and%20publicise%20data%20on%20how%20many%20children%20get%20unwanted%20sexual%20advances%20on%20their%20apps.%20He%20said%20that%20encrypted%20messages%20are%20%26quot%3Breally%20important%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20people%20but%20he%20was%20less%20sure%20if%20they%20were%20appropriate%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20he%20felt%20children's%20safety%20was%20a%20top%20priority%20at%20Meta%2C%20Mr%20Bejar%20claimed%20that%20dozens%20of%20researchers%20had%20been%20laid%20off%20from%20its%20Instagram%20wellbeing%20team%20since%20he%20left.%20%26quot%3BThat%20tells%20you%20a%20lot%20about%20priorities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700624220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fqqv8pi2_instagram-generic-unsplash_625x300_23_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-is-fundamentally-misleading-public-about-instagram-safety-claims-ex-employee-4594954%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Meta%20executive%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20social%20media%20firm%20is%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20misleading%26quot%3B%20the%20public%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20its%20photo-sharing%20app%20Instagram%20for%20teens.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-is-fundamentally-misleading-public-about-instagram-safety-claims-ex-employee-4594954%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-is-fundamentally-misleading-public-about-instagram-safety-claims-ex-employee-4594954%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%