%20taking%20the%20permission%20of%20gram%20sabhas%2C%E2%80%9D%20protesters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F15%2Fauthorities-indifferent-90-days-on-adivasis-from-70-villages-protest-against-mining-in-maharashtras-surjagarh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20%3Cem%3ENewsLaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20June.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20month%20they%20constructed%20a%20police%20station%20at%20Peepliburgi%20and%20have%20plans%20to%20bring%20more%20police%20stations%20at%20Todgatta%2C%20Morewada%2C%20Gardewada%20and%20Jharewada%2C%20among%20others.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecurity%20forces%20constantly%20threaten%20villagers%20over%20their%20opposition%20to%20mining%2C%20interrogating%20them%20on%20their%20whereabouts%20in%20the%20name%20of%20fighting%20Maoists%20or%20Naxalites.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20form%20of%20mental%20harassment%20that%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20decades%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mangesh%20Naroti%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20movement%2C%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1056602%2Fthe-cost-of-protesting-against-mining-in-gadchiroli%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085404%2FIMG-20230725-WA0021.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085404%2FIMG-20230725-WA0021.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085404%2FIMG-20230725-WA0021-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085404%2FIMG-20230725-WA0021-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685787%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Todgatta%20protest%20site%20before%20police%20arrived.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKey%20protesters%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20over%20the%20past%20two%20days%2C%20the%20state%20had%20been%20using%20drone%20cameras%20over%20the%20protest%20site%20to%20ensure%20constant%20surveillance%20over%20the%20region%20and%20peoples%E2%80%99%20activities%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20knew%20the%20exact%20movements%20and%20names%20of%20all%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20protest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMovements%20leaders%20believe%20that%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20crackdown%20was%20a%20timed%20attack%20after%20the%20police%20learnt%20that%20activists%20like%20advocate%20Lalsu%20Nogoti%2C%20along%20with%20Sushila%20Naroti%2C%20Rakesh%20Alam%2C%20Poonam%20Jetti%2C%20Vandu%20Uike%2C%20and%20Sainu%20Hichami%20would%20be%20travelling%20to%20represent%20their%20movement%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20and%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India.%20The%20conference%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CAnti-Displacement%20Movement%20and%20State%20Repression%E2%80%9D%20and%20organised%20by%20the%20Forum%20Against%20Corporatisation%20and%20Militarisation%20(FACAM)%2C%20saw%20powerful%20statements%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20a%20detailed%20booklet%20outlining%20the%20issues%20of%20mining%20and%20repression%2C%20and%20resistance%20in%20Surjagarh%20was%20released.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20Jetti%2C%20a%20village%20Sarpanch%2C%20spoke%20about%20how%20any%20act%20of%20questioning%20mining%20or%20police%20activities%20leads%20to%20being%20labelled%20as%20%E2%80%9CNaxal%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CMaoist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Nogoti%20stated%20that%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20is%20often%20mis-labelled%20as%20%E2%80%9CNaxal-sponsored%E2%80%9D%20to%20hide%20a%20nexus%20of%20crony%20capitalism%20that%20trickles%20down%20to%20local%20administration%20and%20affects%20villagers%20most%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20protest%20now%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20brutal%20suppression%20came%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20after%20the%20protest%20and%20demands%20at%20Todgatta%20were%20voiced%20internationally%20on%20October%208%2C%202023%20by%20advocate%20Nogoti%2C%20at%20the%2054th%20Session%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(UNHRC)%2C%20at%20Geneva%20in%20Switzerland.%20Nogoti%20spoke%20through%20a%20video%20statement%20in%20a%20General%20Debate%20Council%20Meeting%20under%20Agenda%20Item%209%2C%20which%20covers%20Durban%20Declaration%20and%20Program%20of%20Action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20six%20proposed%20mines%20spanning%204%2C684%20hectares%20were%20recently%20leased%20through%20a%20composite%20mining%20lease%20to%20five%20companies%3A%20Omsairam%20Steels%20and%20Alloys%20Private%20Limited%2C%20JSW%20Steels%20Limited%2C%20Sunflag%20Iron%20and%20Steel%20Company%20Limited%2C%20Universal%20Industrial%20Equipment%20and%20Technical%20Services%20Private%20Limited%2C%20and%20Natural%20Resources%20Energy%20Private%20Limited.%20All%20six%20mines%20encroach%20upon%20the%20land%20already%20granted%20to%20people%20from%20surrounding%20Adivasi%20villages%20as%20part%20of%20their%20community%20forest%20rights%20land%20under%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%2C%202006.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F06%2F15%2Fauthorities-indifferent-90-days-on-adivasis-from-70-villages-protest-against-mining-in-maharashtras-surjagarh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20local%20study%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20at%20least%2040%2C900%20people%20will%20be%20displaced%20if%20these%20mines%20come%20into%20existence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20March%2011%2C%202023%2C%20villagers%20from%20across%20the%20Surjagad%20and%20Damkondwahi%20pattis%2Filakas%20(areas)%20have%20been%20indefinitely%20protesting%20under%20the%20banners%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CDamkondawahi%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CSurjagarh%20Patti%20Paramparik%20Gotul%20Samiti%E2%80%9D.%20The%20protest%20is%20being%20led%20by%20the%20Madia-Gond%20Adivasi%20community%2C%20one%20of%20the%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribal.nic.in%2FDivisionsFiles%2FSwLPVTGs.pdf%5C%22%3EParticularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Groups%20(PVTG)%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20state.%20Representatives%20from%20over%2070%20villages%20have%20been%20taking%20turns%20to%20occupy%20a%20stretch%20of%20land%20in%20Todgatta%2C%20thereby%20making%20the%20resistance%20viable%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085315%2FIMG-20230725-WA0176.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085315%2FIMG-20230725-WA0176.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085315%2FIMG-20230725-WA0176-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085315%2FIMG-20230725-WA0176-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685783%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20red%20waters%20of%20Todgatta.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20huge%20intergenerational%20and%20cross-regional%20impacts%20on%20an%20entire%20way%20of%20life%2C%20knowledge%20systems%2C%20and%20illegal%20dispossession%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejal%2C%20jangal%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20are%20also%20many%20health%20related%20impacts%20of%20the%20mines%20that%20people%20are%20protesting%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EImpact%20of%20the%20iron-ore%20mines%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lloyd%E2%80%99s%20iron-ore%20mine%20has%20had%20a%20tremendous%20impact%20on%20agriculture%2C%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20the%20health%20of%20Surjagarh%E2%80%99s%20residents.%20The%20region%20is%20polluted%20by%20red%20iron%20oxide%20discharge%2C%20chemical%20effluents%2C%20and%20large%20amounts%20of%20debris.%20The%20fresh%20water%20in%20the%20region%20has%20turned%20red%20and%20is%20unusable%20and%20agricultural%20fields%20are%20overrun%20by%20silt.%20An%20Adivasi%20farmer%2C%20Ajay%20Toppo%2C%20died%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findependence-mining-gadchiroli-adivasi-protest-maharashtra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuicide%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202022%2C%20after%20what%20many%20believe%20was%20prolonged%20suffering%20he%20underwent%20due%20to%20the%20changes%20in%20his%20farmland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20been%20known%20to%20suffer%20from%20various%20diseases%20such%20as%20catharsis%2C%20dehydration%20and%20gastro-intestinal%20irritation.%20Locals%20say%20iron%20ore%20can%20interfere%20with%20normal%20body%20fluid%20regulation%20even%20long%20after%20a%20mine%20has%20been%20closed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnj.gov%2Fhealth%2Feoh%2Frtkweb%2Fdocuments%2Ffs%2F1036.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20hazardous%20effects%20of%20iron%20oxide%20on%20human%20health%2C%20exposure%20to%20iron%20oxide%20fumes%20and%20iron%20ore%20dust%20can%20cause%20metal%20fume%20fever%2C%20which%20is%20a%20flu-like%20illness%20with%20symptoms%20of%20metallic%20taste%2C%20fever%20and%20chills%2C%20aches%2C%20chest%20tightness%20and%20cough.%20Moreover%2C%20prolonged%20or%20repeated%20contact%20can%20discolour%20the%20eyes%20causing%20permanent%20Iron%20staining.%20Repeated%20exposure%20to%20iron%20oxide%20fumes%20or%20dust%20could%20also%20cause%20pneumoconiosis%20(siderosis)%20with%20cough%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20reported%20that%20the%20iron%20contamination%20has%20also%20affected%20the%20health%20of%20animals%20and%20livestock%2C%20and%20has%20therefore%2C%20severely%20impacted%20livelihood%20and%20income.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnjali%20is%20a%20cultural%20activist%20learning%20with%20indigenous%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20a%20part%20of%20Yugma%20Collective.%20Shubha%20is%20a%20member%20of%20Yugma%20Collective%20and%20is%20currently%20studying%20the%20legal%20aspects%20of%20forest-based%20movements.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700623821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22085351%2FIMG-20231120-WA0010.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgadchiroli-maharashtra-mining-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20movements'%20leaders%20had%20allegedly%20been%20surveilled%20and%20were%20beaten%20up%20brutally%20on%20the%20day.%20Several%20of%20the%20protesters'%20huts%20were%20burnt%20and%20their%20belongings%20taken.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgadchiroli-maharashtra-mining-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korea%20to%20suspend%20part%20of%20military%20pact%20after%20North%20claims%20spy%20satellite%20launch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700623725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105402116%2Cimgsize-69484.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworl