eport%2C%20these%20closures%20and%20alterations%20to%20mosque%20architecture%20are%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20called%20%26quot%3Bconsolidation%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20exerting%20control%20over%20religious%20practices.%20The%20Chinese%20government's%20actions%20have%20been%20criticized%20for%20suppressing%20Islam%20and%20contradicting%20their%20claim%20of%20merely%20consolidating%20mosques.%20The%20report%20reveals%20that%20over%201%2C300%20mosques%20in%20Ningxia%20have%20been%20closed%20since%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeyond-xinjiang-china-closing-destroying-hundreds-of-mosques-in-northern-regions%2Farticleshow%2F105401373.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeyond-xinjiang-china-closing-destroying-hundreds-of-mosques-in-northern-regions%2Famp_articleshow%2F105401373.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fbeyond-xinjiang-china-closing-destroying-hundreds-of-mosques-in-northern-regions%2Famp_articleshow%2F105401373.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''Hurts%20To%20See%20This''%3A%20Anand%20Mahindra%20On%20Garbage%20Dumping%20Video%20In%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndustrialist%20Anand%20Mahindra%2C%20who%20is%20quite%20active%20on%20Twitter%20regularly%20posts%20about%20trending%20topics%20and%20engaging%20stories%2C%20for%20his%2010.8%20million%20followers.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20reacted%20to%20a%20viral%20video%20of%C2%A0people%20dumping%20trash%20into%20the%20sea%20near%20Gateway%20of%20India%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%C2%A0business%20tycoon%20expressed%20his%20anger%20and%20displeasure%20over%20the%20actions%20of%20people%20in%20the%20viral%20clip%20and%20blamed%20the%20careless%20civic%20attitude.%20Notably%2C%20the%20video%20shows%20two%20men%20emptying%20gunny%20bags%20containing%20trash-%20mainly%20flowers-%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20near%20the%20iconic%20structure%20in%20south%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It%20hurts%20just%20to%20see%20this.%20No%20amount%20of%20improvement%20in%20physical%20infrastructure%20can%20improve%20the%20city's%20quality%20of%20life%20if%20the%20civic%20attitude%20isn't%20transformed%2C''%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20November%2021.%20He%20also%20tagged%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Greater%20Mumbai%20and%20Mumbai%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20hurts%20just%20to%20see%20this.%20No%20amount%20of%20improvement%20in%20physical%20infrastructure%20can%20improve%20the%20city's%20quality%20of%20life%20if%20the%20civic%20attitude%20isn't%20transformed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIqbalSinghChah2%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IqbalSinghChah2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMumbaiPolice%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MumbaiPolice%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEfh0ssHQ3f%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEfh0ssHQ3f%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20anand%20mahindra%20(%40anandmahindra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanandmahindra%2Fstatus%2F1726855930548228209%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20video%20clip%20that%20sparked%20outrage%20online%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20and%20Mumbai%20police%20launched%20a%20search%20for%20the%20man.%20He%20was%20traced%20and%20identified%20after%20tracking%20the%20taxi%20in%20which%20he%20had%20reached%20the%20Gateway%20of%20India%2C%20according%20to%20a%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20civic%20body.%C2%A0After%20tracing%20him%2C%20officials%20of%20the%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Department%20slapped%20a%C2%A0%E2%82%B9%C2%A010%2C000%20penalty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20drew%20strong%20reactions%20from%20internet%20users%20and%20public%20representatives%20who%20demanded%20action%20against%20the%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Mr%20Mahindra's%20tweet%2C%20one%20person%20wrote%2C%20''Absolutely%2C%20the%20soul%20of%20a%20city%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20its%20structures%20but%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20its%20people.%20A%20collective%20shift%20in%20people's%20attitude%2C%20responsibility%2C%20and%20pride%20can%20truly%20elevate%20a%20city's%20quality%20of%20life.%20Here's%20to%20hoping%20for%20a%20positive%20change!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Easy%20access%20to%20properly%20dispose%20garbage%20should%20be%20arranged%20across%20all%20cities%20and%20people%20need%20to%20be%20educated%20via%20tv%2C%20social%20media%20and%20hoardings%20about%20waste%20disposal.Govt%20should%20spend%20enough%20resources%20to%20fix%20this%20the%20same%20way%20they%20did%20implementing%20UPI%2Fdigital%20payments.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''We%20punish%20traffic%20violation%20and%20possibly%20save%201%20life%20per%20misdemeanor.%20But%20we%20let%20such%20violations%20in%20open%20public%20go%20Scott%20free.%20They%20endanger%20whole%20community%2Fcity%20and%20ultimately%20earth%20per%20misdemeanor.%20And%20there%20are%20countless%20ways%20it's%20done.%20It's%20high%20time%20there%20are%20strict%20n%20heavy%20fines%20on%20environmental%20offender.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''I%20completely%20agree%20with%20you.%20It's%20essential%20for%20individuals%20and%20the%20community%20to%20prioritize%20and%20foster%20a%20positive%20civic%20attitude%20for%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20the%20city.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700622780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F9m9456ho_anand-mahindra-_625x300_05_June_23.jpg%22%2C%