has%20put%20the%20future%20of%20OpenAI%20in%20doubt%2C%20even%20as%20the%20technology%20it%20champions%20is%20poised%20to%20flourish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Microsoft's%20interest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20been%20an%20OpenAI%20partner%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20startup%20and%20weaving%20its%20innovations%20into%20Microsoft%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComputing%20power%20hosted%20in%20the%20cloud%20at%20Microsoft%20data%20centers%20has%20been%20essential%20to%20training%20large-scale%20language%20models%2C%20making%20possible%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20released%20a%20year%20ago%20for%20public%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20infused%20ChatGPT%20technology%20into%20software%20like%20Word%20and%20Outlook%20sold%20to%20customers%2C%20and%20into%20its%20Bing%20search%20engine%20that%20has%20long%20struggled%20to%20compete%20with%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20investments%20have%20bought%20it%20a%20stake%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20remains%20controlled%20by%20the%20original%20nonprofit%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%2C%20Microsoft%20was%20not%20informed%20about%20the%20OpenAI%20board's%20decision%20to%20fire%20Altman%20on%20Friday%20and%20oust%20co-founder%20Greg%20Brockman%20from%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20shocking%20move%20remained%20unclear%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20some%20believe%20it%20involved%20a%20fear%20OpenAI%20was%20moving%20too%20quickly%20and%20straying%20from%20its%20mission%20of%20making%20sure%20artificial%20intelligence%20benefits%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20an%20Altman%20comeback%20possible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20quickly%20moved%20to%20hire%20Altman%2C%20announcing%20a%20deal%20to%20have%20him%20join%20the%20Redmond%2C%20Washington-based%20computing%20colossus%20to%20lead%20a%20new%20artificial%20intelligence%20tea