22Israel's%20cabinet%20approves%20hostage%20deal%20in%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225118%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel%20supporters%20take%20part%20in%20a%20demonstration%20demanding%20immediate%20release%20of%20children%20hostages%20who%20are%20being%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%20Hamas%2C%20in%20Prague%2C%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20November%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655ccb9a9c7d23cb3b9df6ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223412%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsrael%20supporters%20take%20part%20in%20a%20demonstration%20demanding%20immediate%20release%20of%20children%20hostages%20who%20are%20being%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%20Hamas%2C%20in%20Prague%2C%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20November%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FDavid%20W%20Cerny%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsrael's%20government%20has%20approved%20a%20hostage%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%20amid%20the%20war.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20outline%20includes%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages%20who%20are%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20comes%20as%20Israeli%20forces%20continue%20their%20extensive%20ground%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20cabinet%20approved%20a%20hostage%20release%20deal%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20local%20time%2C%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%20that%20comes%20more%20than%20six%20weeks%20into%20the%20devastating%20war%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Israel's%20government%20said%20it%20approved%20the%20outline%20of%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20an%20agreement%20that%20will%20see%20the%20release%20of%2050%20hostages%20who%20were%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20during%20its%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20four-day%20ceasefire.%20The%20government%20added%20that%20the%20pause%20in%20fighting%20would%20extend%20for%20one%20day%20for%20every%2010%20hostages%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20150%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20by%20Israel%20would%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20and%20the%20security%20services%20will%20continue%20the%20war%20in%20order%20to%20return%20home%20all%20of%20the%20hostages%2C%20complete%20the%20elimination%20of%20Hamas%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20new%20threat%20to%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20from%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tentative%20agreement%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20exactly%20when%20the%20hostage%20and%20prisoner%20exchange%20will%20be%20completed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Flive-blog%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-updates-rcna126110%23rcrd26266%5C%22%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20the%20families%20of%20hostages%20will%20have%2024%20hours%20to%20appeal%20to%20Israel's%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20object%20to%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20groundbreaking%20development%20follows%20weeks%20of%20intense%20negotiations%20and%20high-level%20engagement%20involving%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Egypt%2C%20a%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20deal%20involves%20only%20the%2050%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20pause%20in%20fighting%20could%20be%20extended%20if%20Hamas%20releases%20more%20hostages%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20holding%20around%20240%20hostages%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Israelis%2C%20Americans%2C%20and%20other%20foreign%20nationals%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20captured%20during%20the%20militant%20group's%20brutal%20rampage%2C%20which%20left%20over%201%2C200%20people%20dead.%20The%20Israeli%20government%20has%20been%20under%20widespread%20domestic%20pressure%20to%20secure%20their%20release%2C%20while%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20have%20sprouted%20in%20major%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%20with%20the%20hostages%20and%20their%20families.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20meets%20with%20soldiers%20as%20he%20visits%20an%20Israeli%20army%20base%20in%20Tze'elim%2C%20Israel%20November%207%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d2b689c7d23cb3b9e7f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22987%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20meets%20with%20soldiers%20as%20he%20visits%20an%20Israeli%20army%20base%20in%20Tze'elim%2C%20Israel%20November%207%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Government%20Press%20Office%2FHaim%20Zach%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20provided%20Israel%20with%20both%20diplomatic%20support%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-mq-9-reaper-drones-gaza-searching-hamas-hostages-2023-11%5C%22%3Eaerial%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20with%20its%20hostage%20recovery%20efforts.%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20Spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20was%20working%20%26quot%3Bhour%20by%20hour%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20everything%20we%20can%26quot%3B%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsraeliPM%2Fstatus%2F1726964284260012443%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20between%206%20p.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%20local%20time%20he%20will%20convene%20the%20country's%20war%20cabinet%2C%20security%20cabinet%2C%20and%20government%2C%20in%20three%20separate%20meetings.%20The%20office%20said%20the%20announcement%20comes%20%26quot%3Bin%20light%20of%20developments%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20release%20of%20our%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20indicating%20that%20a%20deal%20may%20be%20in%20reach.%20Four%20hostages%20have%20already%20been%20released%20from%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmi%20Palmor%2C%20who%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20director%20general%20of%20Israel's%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20and%20has%20experience%20on%20a%20hostage%20negotiation%20team%2C%20said%20this%20could%20end%20up%20being%20the%20only%20deal%20that%20the%20country%20manages%20to%20reach%20with%20Hamas%2C%20and%20its%20also%20uncertain%20if%20the%20militant%20group%20will%20actually%20honor%20its%20agreements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20its%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20decisions%20are%20extremely%20difficult%20and%20it's%20a%20risk%20management%20because%2C%20I%20think%20that%20even%20without%20saying%20this%2C%20everyone%20understands%20that%20we%20are%20playing%20with%20the%20devil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Israeli%20soldier%20rides%20in%20a%20tank%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20ground%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20this%20handout%20image%20released%20November%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d2b1b4ca513d8242d5753%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli%20soldier%20rides%20in%20a%20tank%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20ground%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20this%20handout%20image%20released%20November%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%2FHandout%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20ongoing%20fighting%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Israeli%20officials%20vow%20will%20continue%20until%20Hamas%20is%20ultimately%20destroyed%20%E2%80%94%20will%20play%20out%20remains%20unclear.%20The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20is%20several%20weeks%20into%20its%20ground%20offensive%20and%20controls%20large%20swaths%20of%20territory%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20while%20its%20warplanes%20continue%20to%20bombard%20the%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20where%20over%2012%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20war%20began%20in%20early%20October.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIDF%20Chief%20of%20the%20General%20Staff%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Herzi%20Halevi%20told%20reserve%20soldiers%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20ground%20operations%20in%20Gaza%20are%20creating%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20conditions%26quot%3B%20for%20bringing%20back%20hostages.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hurts%20Hamas%2C%20it%20creates%20pressure%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20this%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20have%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fas-eu-weighs-ceasefire-call-us-rejects-any-such-push-says-it-only-benefits-hamas%2F%5C%22%3Erejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20growing%20calls%20from%20the%20global%20community%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20with%20the%20White%20House%20arguing%20that%20it%20benefits%20Hamas%20and%20gives%20the%20militant%20group%20time%20to%20regroup.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20has%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20get%20the%20Israelis%20to%20agree%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Fisrael-humanitarian-pauses-gaza-00126355%5C%22%3Eshort%20pauses%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20to%20allow%20for%20civilians%20to%20evacuate%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20facilitate%20the%20movement%20of%20humanitarian%20aid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fighting%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20not%20been%20limited%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20has%20drawn%20in