B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20the%20coworker's%20wife%20%26quot%3Bwas%20bent%20over%20and%20was%20kissing%26quot%3B%20her%20supervisor%20and%20another%20coworker%20simultaneously.%20The%20woman%20who%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%2C%20disgusted%20and%20outraged%26quot%3B%20and%20ran%20outside%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20had%20left%20her%20guacamole%20bowl%20inside%2C%20the%20suit%20says.%20The%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20when%20she%20went%20back%20to%20retrieve%20it%2C%20she%20saw%20her%20supervisor%20and%20a%20coworker%20throwing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20vomited%20in%20the%20trash%2C%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Plaintiff's%20guacamole%20bowl%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleges%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20she%20reported%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20holiday%20party%20to%20Taco%20Bell's%20HR%20department%20and%20Alvarado%20Restaurant%20Group%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20franchise.%20Her%20supervisor%20and%20other%20employees%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20public%20sexual%20encounter%20were%20fired%2C%20the%20suit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20after%20they%20were%20terminated%2C%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%20associated%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20defendants%20%26quot%3Bsmashed%20out%20the%20back%20left%20window%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20car%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Taco%20Bell%20and%20Alvarado%20Restaurant%20Group%20%26quot%3Bdid%20nothing%20about%20these%20threats%20and%20instead%20told%20%5Bher%5D%20that%20they%20were%20transferring%20her%20to%20a%20new%20location%20rather%20than%20disciplining%20the%20employees%20who%20threatened%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20ultimately%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%20actual%2C%20consequential%2C%20and%20incidental%20financial%20losses%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp