n%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20present%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Statistics%2C%20is%20the%20way%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20(CPI)%20and%20the%20wholesale%20price%20index%20(WPI)%20are%20calculated%20and%2C%20specifically%2C%20the%20basket%20of%20goods%20on%20which%20they%20are%20based.%20This%20basket%20has%20not%20changed%20for%2012%20years%2C%20during%20which%20period%20the%20consumption%20patterns%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20have%20changed%20dramatically.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20baskets%20of%20goods%20on%20which%20WPI%20and%20CPI%20are%20based%20are%20now%20almost%20comprehensively%20out%20of%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2050-minute%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sen%20said%20GDP%20and%20the%20GDP%20growth%20figure%20only%20convey%20a%20partial%20picture%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy.%20They%20do%20not%20reveal%20high%20levels%20of%20unemployment%20or%20increasing%20demand%20for%20the%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20scheme%20NREGA%20or%20the%20fact%20that%2058%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20is%20self-employed%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20interprets%20as%20distress%20employment.%20He%20adds%20that%20perhaps%20as%20many%20as%2095%20million%20people%2C%20who%20are%20said%20to%20be%20self-employed%2C%20do%20not%20earn%20any%20income%20at%20all.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20politicians%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sometimes%20economists%20%E2%80%93%20present%20the%20GDP%20growth%20figure%20to%20claim%20the%20country%20is%20soaring%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20capture%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20who%20are%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6lNkA_ZyRWI%3Fsi%3DiBhoYnx3U_9qxoFs%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20says%20he%20believes%20the%20Q1%20GDP%20growth%20figure%20of%207.8%25%20is%20an%20overestimation.%20He%20believes%206.5%25%20is%20more%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20explains%20why%20he%20believes%20the%20recent%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20finding%20that%2058%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20are%20self-employed%20is%20not%20an%20indication%20of%20increasing%20self-entrepreneurship%20(as%20claimed%20by%20SBI%20economists)%20but%20distress%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20substantial%20discussion%20about%20whether%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20right%20to%20claim%20India%20will%20be%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047.%20Sen%20says%20if%20this%20means%20India%20will%20achieve%20the%20World%20Bank%20criteria%20of%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20%2413%2C200%2C%20that%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20possible.%20If%2C%20however%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20means%20India%20will%20reach%20the%20level%20of%20the%20UK%E2%80%99s%20%2445%2C000%2C%20then%20that%20is%20a%20flat%20resounding%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20adds%20that%20even%20if%20you%20reach%20the%20World%20Bank%20criteria%20of%20%2413%2C200%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20India%20could%20still%20have%2050%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20self-employed%20and%20up%20to%20100%20million%20people%20earning%20no%20income%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700575859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21190519%2FKT-21-Nov-.01_01_59_12.Still004.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-pronab-sen-gdp-figure-concern%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Sen%20says%20that%20the%20GDP%20growth%20figure%20only%20conveys%20a%20partial%20picture%20of%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy.%20It%20does%20not%20reveal%20high%20levels%20of%20unemployment%20or%20increasing%20demand%20for%20NREGA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-pronab-sen-gdp-figure-concern%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20This%20JEE%20Topper%20Chose%20to%20Launch%20a%20Startup%20Over%20Accepting%20IIT-B%E2%80%99s%20Placement%20Packages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20night%20before%20the%20JEE%20Mains%20exam%20I%20was%20nervous.%20I%20remember%20calling%20my%20professor%20anxiously.%20He%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Sachin%20Tendulkar%20is%20a%20great%20player.%20But%20even%20if%20he%20fails%20to%20score%20a%20century%20in%20one%20match%2C%20he%20knows%20he%20will%20in%20the%20next%20one.%20He%20trusts%20his%20abilities%20more%20than%20circumstances.%E2%80%99%20The%20day%20of%20the%20exam%20dawned.%20Ninety%20questions%20stared%20at%20me.%20I%20had%20one%20attempt%20and%20I%20had%20to%20make%20it%20count.%20After%201.5%20hours%20of%20solving%20questions%2C%20I%20looked%20to%20see%20how%20far%20I%E2%80%99d%20gotten.%20I%E2%80%99d%20only%20managed%20to%20attempt%2030.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20%E2%80%94%20famous%20for%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains%202017%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20recalls%20that%20moment%20in%20time%2C%20he%20terms%20it%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife-changing%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Although%20flustered%2C%20he%20felt%20he%20knew%20his%20attitude%20determined%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20set%20my%20pen%20down%20and%20closed%20my%20eyes.%20I%20recalled%20all%20the%20exams%20I%20had%20ever%20attempted.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20how%20in%20the%20past%20few%2