visit%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20head%20of%20domestic%20intelligence%20reiterated%20the%20%E2%80%98Five%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20nations%E2%80%99%20backing%20of%20Canada%2C%20stating%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-spy-chief-mike-burgess-canada-nijjar-india-five-eyes%5C%22%3Eno%20reason%20to%20dispute%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20assertions%20regarding%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen.%20The%20%E2%80%98Five%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20network%20is%20an%20intelligence-sharing%20alliance%20that%20comprises%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700574002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21185624%2FF_cqYFtWcAA9C_b.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fforeign-ministers-of-india-australia-discuss-india-canada-dispute%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noting%20that%20Australia%20had%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20strong%20relationship%E2%80%9D%20with%20both%20India%20and%20Canada%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20it%20was%20important%20that%20Australia%20get%20our%20perspective%20on%20the%20issue.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fforeign-ministers-of-india-australia-discuss-india-canada-dispute%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharti%20Airtel%20CEO%20Gopal%20Vittal%20bats%20for%20e-sim%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20customers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700573780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-01%2F29%2Ffull%2F1611865742-4073.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharti-airtel-ceo-gopal-vittal-bats-for-e-sim-in-a-letter-to-customers-123112100948_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22E-SIMs%20also%20allow%20users%20to%20use%20multiple%20mobile%20numbers%20on%20a%20single%20e-SIM%20and%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20change%20devices%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharti-airtel-ceo-gopal-vittal-bats-for-e-sim-in-a-letter-to-customers-123112100948_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharti-airtel-ceo-gopal-vittal-bats-for-e-sim-in-a-letter-to-customers-123112100948_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharti-airtel-ceo-gopal-vittal-bats-for-e-sim-in-a-letter-to-customers-123112100948_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Low%20Production%20Coupled%20With%20Increased%20Imports%20Take%20a%20Toll%20on%20Kashmiri%20Apple%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21174809%2FApples_of_Kashmir_valley.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20July%2016%2C%20when%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20Mohammad%20Yousuf%20Tarigami%20addressed%20the%20first%20national%20conference%20of%20the%20Apple%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India%20(AFFI)%20organised%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Kisaan%20Tehreek%2C%20a%20hard%20rain%20descended%20on%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20town%2C%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20conference.%20However%2C%20hundreds%20of%20apple%20farmers%20sitting%20under%20a%20shaky%20canopy%20did%20not%20move%20an%20inch%20until%20the%20Marxist%20leader%20completed%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarigami%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20halt%20the%20import%20of%20apples%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%2C%20as%20such%20imports%20substantially%20contribute%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20prices%20of%20domestic%20produce.%20Barely%20two%20days%20later%2C%20on%20July%2019%2C%20reports%20emerged%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20decided%20to%20remove%20the%20extra%20tariff%20duty%20on%20Washington%20apples.%20On%20September%205%2C%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%20issued%20an%20order%20waiving%20the%2020%25%20additional%20retaliatory%20duty%20levied%20on%20premium%20Washington%20apples%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20came%20on%20the%20close%20heels%20of%20a%20meeting%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20counterpart%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Tarigami%20issued%20a%20statement%20terming%20the%20removal%20of%20additional%20duty%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20G20%20gift%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20minted%20AFFI%20held%20conferences%20in%20both%20south%20and%20central%20Kashmir%20to%20mount%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%20The%20federation%20also%20put%20forth%20a%20charter%20of%20demands%20before%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20September%2C%20we%20met%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20presented%20him%20a%20memorandum%20of%20demands%20concerning%20apple%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahoor%20Ahamd%20Rather%2C%20president%20of%20AFFI%20(J%26amp%3BK).%20He%20added%20that%20restrictions%20and%20100%25%20import%20duty%20on%20apples%20imported%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%20could%20save%20the%20apple%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20imports%20are%20bound%20to%20affect%20the%20produce%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rather.%3Cbr%3E%5CnKashmir%20produces%20around%20two%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20apples%20annually%2C%20with%20around%203.5%20million%20people%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20relying%20on%20the%20industry%20for%20their%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20cultivators%20in%20the%20Valley%20continue%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns%20over%20the%20import%20of%20apples%20from%20across%20the%20world%20with%20low%20import%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImports%20from%20Iran%2C%20routed%20through%20Afghanistan%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20additional%20duty%20on%20Washington%20premium%20apples%20are%20impacting%20domestic%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohamamd%20Ashraf%20Wani%2C%20a%20local%20fruit%20grower%20and%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Fruit%20Mandi%2C%20Shopian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWani%20said%20that%20Indian%20apples%20could%20not%20compete%20with%20the%20Washington%20premium%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20drew%20an%20analogy%20between%20Indian%20and%20US%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20US%20farmers%20receive%20around%2032%25%20subsidy%20while%20the%20subsidy%20received%20by%20domestic%20farmers%20%5Bin%20India%5D%20stands%20at%20scant%202.5%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Horticulture%20issued%20statements%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20allay%20the%20fears%20of%20farmers%20regarding%20the%20apple%20imports.%20Director%20horticulture%2C%20Ghulam%20Rasool%20Mir%2C%20on%20November%205%20told%20PTI%20that%20imports%20from%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries%20were%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20J%26amp%3B%20K%E2%80%99s%20apple%20industry%20and%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20production%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20apple%20production%20this%20year%20is%20significantly%20lower%2C%20with%20farmers%20from%20the%20apple-rich%20districts%20of%20Kashmir%20reporting%20about%20a%2040%25%20dip%20in%20the%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIzhan%20Javed%2C%20an%20apple%20orchardist%20and%20spokesperson%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Fruit%20and%20Vegetables%20Processing%20and%20Integrated%20Cold%20Chain%20Association%20(JKPICCA)%2C%20said%20that%20the%20low%20production%20was%20coupled%20with%20more%20C-grade%20apples.%20%E2%80%9CAround%2030%25%20is%20of%20lower%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Javed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20erratic%20weather%20conditions%20during%20the%20spring%20are%20largely%20being%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20low%20production%20and%20poor%20quality%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20scientist%20at%20the%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agricultural%20Sciences%20and%20Technology%2C%20Kashmir%20(SKUAST-K)%20Dr%20Tariq%20Rasool%20said%20that%20frequent%20rains%20from%20March%20to%20July%20affected%20the%20fruit%20produce.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20rains%20stymied%20the%20movement%20of%20pollinators%20that%20resulted%20in%20low%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLower%20temperature%20during%20that%20period%20is%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20scientist.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20commonly%20grown%20Delicious%20variety%20%E2%80%9Chas%20an%20alternate%20bearing%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%20we%20experienced%20a%20bumper%20crop%20and%20this%20year%20it%20was%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20drop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20promising%20market%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20apple%20prices%20have%20suddenly%20plummeted%20over%20the%20two%20weeks.%20The%20drop%20in%20the%20prices%20is%20attributed%20to%20the%20arrival%20of%20thousands%20of%20apple%20cartons%20from%20Iran%20in%20Indian%20fruit%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first-rate%20apples%20from%20Iran%20via%20Afghanistan%20have%20precipitated%20the%20price%20drop.%20We%20were%20happy%20as%20the%20rates%20this%20year%20were%20comparatively%20high%2C%20but%20the%20imported%20produce%20has%20again%20started%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20local%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Javed%20Ahmad%2C%20an%20apple%20grower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20an%20apple%20carton%20of%20Grade-A%20was%20sold%20between%20Rs%201%2C300%20and%20Rs%201%2C400%20in%20local%20fruit%20mandis.%20The%20prices%2C%20at%20the%20time%20this%20article%20was%20written%2C%20have%20dipped%20to%20Rs%20850%20to%20Rs%201%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20Grade-B%20apples%20have%20significantly%20fallen%20(from%20Rs%20400-650%20to%20Rs%20250-300).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGulzar%20Bhar%20is%20a%20journalist%20based%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700573417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21174809%2FApples_of_Kashmir_valley.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flow-production-coupled-with-increased-imports-take-a-toll-on-kashmiri-apple-farmers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20cultivators%20in%20the%20Valley%20continue%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns%20over%20the%20import%20of%20apples%20from%20across%20the%20world%20with%20low%20import%20duties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flow-production-coupled-with-increased-imports-take-a-toll-on-kashmiri-apple-farmers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22First%20images%20emerge%20of%20workers%20trapped%20for%20tenth%20day%20in%20road%20tunnel%20collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700573280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-india-tunnel_6367287.jpg%3F20231121082034%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Findia-footage-emerges-of-41-workers-trapped-for-tenth-day-in-road-tunnel-collapse-13012923%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20images%20have%20emerged%20of%2041%20men%20trapped%20for%20a%20tenth%20day%20under%20a%20collapsed%20road%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht