he%20topic%20of%20empathy%20and%20kindness%20for%2010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20graders%20(in%20a%20school%20library)%2C%20I%20was%20packing%20up%20my%20laptop%20when%20the%20very%20pleasant%20and%20cheerful%20library%20assistant%20mentioned%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20have%20such%20conversations%20with%20teenagers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20concurred%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20hate-filled%20environment%20these%20kids%20are%20growing%20up%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20chatted%20a%20bit%20more%20about%20how%20polarised%20society%20is%2C%20the%20lady%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20if%20only%20Muslims%20were%20eradicated%20from%20the%20world%2C%20all%20our%20problems%20would%20be%20solved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20have%20been%20my%20shell-shocked%20expression%20that%20stopped%20her%20mid-sentence.%20With%20a%20sudden%20note%20of%20alarm%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20a%20Muslim%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20bit%20late%20to%20ask%20me%20that%20now%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20responded.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAap%20school%20me%20baithke%20yeh%20keh%20rahe%20hain%3F%20Aur%20vo%20bhi%20library%20may%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20(You%20said%20that%20sitting%20in%20a%20school%20and%20that%20too%2C%20in%20a%20library%3F)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESlightly%20flustered%2C%20the%20lady%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20true%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20Look%20back%20at%20Indian%20history.%20All%20terrorists%20have%20always%20been%20Muslims%2C%20haven%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrying%20to%20keep%20my%20voice%20steady%20(for%20this%20sort%20of%20bigotry%20never%20fails%20to%20startle)%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20Muslim%20who%20killed%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20true%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20have%20Muslims%20done%20to%20you%20personally%20that%20you%20hate%20them%20so%20much%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20hate%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20is%20the%20image%20that%20is%20created%20of%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20you%20are%20letting%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20become%20your%20reality!%E2%80%9D%20I%20said%2C%20making%20a%20massive%20effort%20to%20stay%20calm.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20living%20in%20a%20country%20whose%20constitution%20honours%20all%20citizens%20equally%2C%20ma%E2%80%99am.%20You%20cannot%20make%20statements%20like%20this%2C%20especially%20not%20in%20a%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20judging%20by%20the%20blank%20and%20uncomprehending%20look%20on%20her%20face%2C%20I%20might%20as%20well%20have%20been%20speaking%20in%20some%20ancient%20and%20unknown%20dialect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20library%2C%20I%20remembered%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJQS-_9K5-Dk%3Fsi%3DpocYAj7L8Fxo9pdU%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espeech%20I%20had%20seen%20on%20YouTube%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20just%20the%20previous%20evening.%20It%20was%20an%20address%20given%20by%20the%20Israeli%20journalist%2C%20Gideon%20Levy%2C%20in%20Washington%20D.C.%20in%202016.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20had%20said%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20have%20a%20dialogue%20today%20with%20most%20Israelis%2C%20even%20for%20me%2C%20is%20an%20impossible%20job.%20Many%20times%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20(talking%20to)%20ordinary%20Israelis%2C%20good%20people.%20They%20would%20volunteer%20anywhere.%20But%20when%20you%20start%20to%20talk%20to%20them%20about%20the%20Occupation%2C%20after%20two%20minutes%20you%20want%20to%20tear%20your%20hair%20out!%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do!%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20to%20start!%20The%20brainwashing%20is%20so%20deep%2C%20and%20the%20denial%20is%20so%20deep!%20And%20the%20ignorance!%20They%20know%20nothing!%20Anyone%20in%20this%20hall%20knows%20so%20much%20more%20about%20the%20Occupation%20than%20the%20average%20Israelis%20(who)%20know%20nothing%2C%20and%20what%20they%20know%20is%20wrong!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELevy%20might%20as%20well%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20the%20average%20mainstream-media-nourished%20Indian%2C%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20whom%20I%20had%20just%20encountered.%20The%20most%20disturbing%20facet%20of%20the%20conversation%20with%20this%20lady%20was%20how%20pleasantly%20earnest%20she%20was%20in%20her%20bigotry.%20There%20was%20no%20anger%2C%20no%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ead-hominem%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20attack%2C%20just%20a%20very%20sincere%20belief%20that%20an%20entire%20community%20of%20Indians%20is%20intrinsically%20evil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20else%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20might%20be%2C%20it%20will%20most%20certainly%20include%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20entire%20sub-stratum%20of%20society%20that%2C%20under%20his%20watch%2C%20genuinely%20believed%20that%20a%20whole%20community%20in%20India%20was%20fundamentally%20bad.%20This%20ecosystem%20was%20nurtured%20by%20a%20steady%20injection%20of%20hate%20and%20misinformation%2C%20not%20unlike%20the%20drip%20irrigation%20methods%20that%20desert%20nations%20often%20employ.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20damage%20that%20has%20been%20done%20to%20the%20minds%20and%20hearts%20of%20millions%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20is%20deep.%20It%20will%20take%20time%20to%20heal%2C%20recover%20and%20rebuild.%20One%20hopes%20and%20prays%20that%20the%20results%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20(both%20at%20the%20state%20and%20at%20the%20national%20level)%20will%20create%20an%20opportunity%20for%20facts%20and%20empathy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20antidotes%20to%20misinformation%20and%20bigotry%20%E2%80%93%20to%20somehow%20enter%20the%20national%20discourse%20once%20again%20in%20a%20steady%2C%20sustained%2C%20and%20significant%20manner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alternative%20is%20too%20horrific%20to%20contemplate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20set%20up%20libraries%20%E2%80%93%20however%20small%20%E2%80%93%20with%20books%20that%20will%20keep%20our%20minds%20and%20hearts%20open%2C%20and%20let%E2%80%99s%20keep%20sharing%20with%20others%20what%20we%20have%20learned%20from%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERohit%20Kumar%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20author%2C%20and%20independent%20journalist%2C%20and%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aletsempathize%40gmail.com%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eletsempathize%40gmail.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700568337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21163929%2Flibrary.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-bigot-in-the-library%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20damage%20that%20has%20been%20done%20to%20the%20minds%20and%20hearts%20of%20millions%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20is%20deep.%20It%20will%20take%20time%20to%20heal%2C%20recover%20and%20rebuild.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-bigot-in-the-library%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Juggling%20Motherhood%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%201st%20MasterChef%20Contestant%20Over