betterindia.com%2F298516%2Fengineer-quits-job-to-make-natural-baby-food-mixes-earns-lakhs-tummy-friendly-sridevi-ashala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20children.%20While%20pursuing%20her%20doctorate%2C%20she%20also%20juggled%20the%20responsibility%20of%20making%20homemade%20food%20for%20her%20firstborn%2C%20her%20daughter%2C%20who%20was%20three%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20looking%20for%20some%20healthy%20food%20to%20serve%20as%20snacks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20market%20in%20search%20of%20some%20unadulterated%20food.%20All%20I%20saw%20was%20frozen%20and%20packaged%20food%2C%20which%20was%20highly%20processed%20with%20many%20preservatives%20and%20harmful%20additives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rukhsaar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailing%20to%20find%20anything%20appealing%2C%20she%20thought%20of%20working%20on%20something%20without%20preservatives%2C%20for%20busy%20mothers.%20After%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20she%20started%20researching%20how%20to%20make%20healthy%20frozen%20snacks%20without%20additives%20and%20started%20experimenting%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20frozen%20chicken%20nuggets%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20They%20are%20all%20loaded%20with%20additives%20and%20meat%20fillers.%20I%20worked%20on%20how%20to%20preserve%20food%20in%20a%20natural%20way%20and%20studied%20how%20to%20increase%20the%20shelf%20life.%20My%20degree%20helped%20in%20recipe%20formulation%20and%20standardisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20took%20her%20almost%20eight%20months%20to%20study%20and%20work%20on%20the%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20experimented%20with%20chicken%20strips%2C%20nuggets%2C%20popcorn%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekalari%20%3C%2Fem%3Echeese%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20became%20a%20big%20hit.%20She%20also%20served%20her%20snacks%20at%20an%20exhibition%20at%20the%20Sheri%20Kashmir%20International%20Convention%20Centre%20(SKICC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20convert%20her%20experiments%20at%20home%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20venture.%20On%203%20August%2C%202019%2C%20she%20launched%20%E2%80%98Khalis%20Foods%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%2C%20frozen%20food%20venture%20from%20Pampore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20life%20had%20other%20plans.%20Just%20three%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20revoked%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20This%20move%20led%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20and%20mobile%20services%2C%20halting%20Rukhsaar%E2%80%99s%20venture%20before%20it%20could%20even%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvwrbofNevi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvwrbofNevi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvwrbofNevi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dr.%20RUKHSAAR%20SAYEED%20%7C%20KHALIS%20FOODS%20(%40khalis_foods)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20mobile%20network.%20As%20my%20business%20was%20online%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20connect%20to%20my%20customers.%20We%20were%20even%20asked%20to%20evacuate%20the%20SKICC%20exhibition.%20All%20my%20frozen%20food%20turned%20bad%20as%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20freezers.%20I%20lost%20about%20Rs%2070%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20to%20be%20bogged%20down%2C%20she%20restarted%20Khalis%20Foods%20in%20November%202020.%20However%2C%20January%202021%20brought%20on%20yet%20another%20COVID%20lockdown%2C%20causing%20her%20to%20shut%20down%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20Rukshaar%20proved%20her%20resilience%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20this%20affect%20her%20vision%20to%20provide%20healthy%2C%20unadulterated%20food%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPursuing%20a%20dream%20is%20never%20easy.%20It%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20especially%20in%20Kashmir.%20My%20passion%20to%20set%20up%20my%20own%20venture%20and%20provide%20unadulterated%2C%20safe%20and%20healthy%20snacking%20options%20for%20my%20people%20is%20all%20that%20keeps%20me%20going.%20If%20I%20fail%20again%20and%20have%20to%20start%20from%20scratch%2C%20I%20will%20do%20it%20all%20again%20in%20a%20heartbeat.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20producing%20quality%20products%20no%20matter%20what%20challenges%20come%20my%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20kept%20her%20going%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201055px)%20100vw%2C%201055px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frukshaar4-1700564126.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221055%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C