%20used%20in%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20employs%20six%20people%20and%20gets%20about%20600%20to%20700%20orders%20per%20month%2C%20she%20informs.%20While%20her%20initial%20focus%20was%20just%20on%20online%20sales%2C%20the%20demand%20led%20her%20to%20sell%20her%20products%20in%20departmental%20stores%20in%20Srinagar%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20focus%20on%20keeping%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290986%2Fhemapriya-natesan-sathumaavu-traditional-powder-for-babies-no-sugar-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20clean%3C%2Fa%3E%20leads%20to%20a%20problem%20of%20storage%20as%20it%20has%20a%20short%20shelf%20life.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20overwhelming%20demand%20for%20our%20products%2C%20but%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20expand%20currently%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20cold%20chains%2C%20refrigerated%20vans%2C%20etc.%20My%20focus%20is%20on%20quality%20and%20I%20will%20not%20compromise%20on%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hopes%20to%20expand%20out%20of%20her%20small%20room%20and%20open%20a%20culinary%20school%20in%20Kashmir%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Kashmiri%20cuisine%20to%20the%20World%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201179px)%20100vw%2C%201179px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rukhsaar%20wants%20people%20to%20know%20about%20Kashmiri%20ingredients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699.jpeg%201179w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-300x232.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-500x386.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-768x593.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRukhsaar3-1700487699-150x116.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334519%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERukhsaar%20innovates%20different%20dishes%20using%20traditional%20Kashmiri%20ingredients.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Khalis%20Foods%20is%20thriving%2C%20Rukhsaar%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20audition%20for%20MasterChef%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20talk%20about%20Kashmiri%20cuisine%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20%3Cem%3Ewazwan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Erogan%20josh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Through%20MasterChef%20India%2C%20I%20want%20the%20country%20to%20know%20how%20we%20prepare%20homemade%20food%20in%20Kashmir.%20We%20use%20so%20many%20local%20indigenous%20ingredients%20to%20make%20our%20food%20and%20there%20is%20a%20science%20behind%20every%20ingredient%20used.%20The%20world%20must%20know%20Kashmiri%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98ghar%20ka%20khana%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshe%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERukhsaar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20eight%20finalists%20in%20MasterChef%20India-Hindi%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Kashmiri%20women%20on%20the%20show.%20She%E2%80%99s%20been%20%E2%80%98wow%E2%80%99ing%20the%20judges%20with%20her%20dishes%2C%20where%20she%20uses%20traditional%20Kashmiri%20ingredients%20in%20creative%2C%20restaurant-quality%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20chef%20thanks%20to%20MasterChef.%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20done%20it%20all%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20one%20of%20the%20few%20Kashmiri%20women%20chefs%2C%20Rukhsaar%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20inspiration%20for%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20valley.%20She%20urges%20youngsters%20to%20follow%20their%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20career%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20my%20passion%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20youngsters%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20to%20transform%20their%20passion%20into%20a%20career.%20Have%20faith%20in%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20her%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98aha%20%3C%2Fem%3Emoment%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20day%20she%20felt%20%E2%80%98she%20made%20it%E2%80%99%2C%20despite%20achieving%20so%20much%2C%20Rukhsaar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20day%20is%20yet%20to%20come%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332580%2Fmillet-based-startups-helping-farmers-ragi-jowar-international-year-of-millet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20in%20a%20good%20place%20and%20very%20grateful%20for%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20received%20so%20far.%20But%20I%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20do.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20everything%20I%E2%80%99ve%20truly%20ever%20wanted%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20wait%20to%20see%20the%20heights%20that%20this%20fiery%20woman%20reaches%2C%20you%20can%20follow%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkhalis_foods%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20place%20orders%2C%20or%20just%20be%20a%20bystander%20to%20witness%20her%20incredible%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700568317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334496%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Rukhsaar%20Sayeed%20from%20Pampore%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20started%20%E2%80%98Khalis%20Foods%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20food%20company%20offering%20homemade%20preservative-free%20frozen%20items%20for%20all%20ages.%20Her%20love%20for%20cooking%20took%20her%20to%20MasterChef%20India%2C%20where%20she%E2%80%99s%20sharing%20authentic%20Kashmiri%20cuisine%20with%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334496%2Fkashmir-rukhsaar-sayeed-masterchef-india-chef-khalis-frozen-foods%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Failed%20Promises%20and%20Tokenism%3A%20Why%20Modi's%20Renewed%20Tribal%20Push%20Doesn't%20Exude%20Confidence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21172235%2FThe-Wire-83.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20special%20focus%20on%20Adivasis%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20missed%20in%20this%20election%20season.%20In%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20campaign%20speeches%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20even%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20emphasised%20that%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20tribal%20society%2C%20even%20going%20so%20far%20as%20to%20declare%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20strived%20hard%20to%20integrate%20the%20Adivasis%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20development%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20treated%20them%20as%20mere%20vote%20banks%20all%20these%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2015%2C%20two%20days%20before%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20went%20to%20polls%2C%20Modi%20announced%20schemes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-can-modis-tribal-push-help-bjp-regain-in-st-seats-where-it-suffered-losses-in-2018%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eworth%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20tribal%20welfare%20on%20the%20occasion.%20The%20announcement%20came%20on%20the%20day%20which%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20earlier%20declared%20as%20%E2%80%98Janjatiya%20Gaurav%20Diwas%E2%80%99%20to%20mark%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Adivasi%20freedom%20fighter%20Birsa%20Munda.%20A%20week%20earlier%2C%20Modi%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20made%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsonair.gov.in%2FNews%3Ftitle%3DBJP-government-at-Centre-has-made-a-five-fold-increase-in-budget-for-welfare-of-tribal-society%253A-Senior-BJP-leader-and-Prime-Minister-Narendra-Modi%26id%3D470875%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSenior%2520BJP%2520leader%2520and%2520Prime%2Cthe%2520top%2520priority%2520of%2520BJP.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20five-fold%20increase%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20budget%20for%20tribal%20welfare%2C%20although%20the%20increase%20is%20proportional%20to%20the%20overall%20jump%20in%20budgetary%20allocations%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20significance%20of%20Adivasis%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20can%20be%20gauged%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20all%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states%2C%20Adivasis%20form%20a%20sizeable%20chunk%20and%20swing%20outcomes.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Adivasis%20constitute%2021%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20according%20to%20Census%202011%2C%20and%20have%2047%20out%20of%20the%20230%20assembly%20seats%20reserved%20for%20them.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Adivasis%20have%20a%20commanding%20position%20with%2030%25%20and%2029%20reserved%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2090.%20Rajasthan%20has%20nearly%2013.5%25%20Adivasis%2C%20but%20they%20are%20concentrated%20in%20pockets%20to%20influence%20the%20outcome%20in%20the%20Mewar%20region.%20Twenty%20five%20seats%20of%20the%20200-member%20assembly%20are%20reserved%20for%20Adivasi%20candidates.%20Although%20the%20number%20of%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Telangana%20is%20nine%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20119%2C%20the%20Adivasis%20still%20form%20around%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-can-modis-tribal-push-help-bjp-regain-in-st-seats-where-it-suffered-losses-in-2018%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20Can%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Push%20Help%20BJP%20Recover%20in%20ST%20Seats%20Where%20it%20Suffered%20Losses%20in%202018%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEver%20since%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20he%20has%20made%20similar%20announcements%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20especially%20during%20election%20campaigns.%20The%20BJP%20has%20counted%20the%20nomination%20of%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India%20as%20its%20biggest%20achievement%20in%20empowering%20Adivasis.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20invoked%20Adivasi%20icons%20in%20election%20campaigns%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20political%20memory.%20While%20declaring%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cborn%20to%20serve%20tribals%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20at%20a%20recent%20election%20rally%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Bishrampur%20asked%20whether%20anyone%20had%20ever%20imagined%20that%20a%20tribal%20woman%20would%20become%20the%20President%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Similarly%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20creating%20new%20Hindu%20icons%20among%20communities%2C%20Modi%20also%20recently%20recalled%20the%20role%20of%20tribal%20freedom%20fighter%20Govind%20Guru%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Banswara.%20Later%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Seoni%2C%20he%20also%20reminded%20people%20that%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20had%20created%20a%20separate%20ministry%20for%20tribal%20affairs.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20been%20recounting%20the%20bravery%20of%20tribal%20icons%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FFeaturesDeatils.aspx%3FNoteId%3D151692%26ModuleId%3D2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGond%20queen%20Rani%20Durgavati%20or%20Rani%20Kamalapati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Habibganj%20railway%20station%20of%20Bhopal%20was%20also%20renamed%20as%20Rani%20Kamalapati%20station%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Adivasi%20activists%20believes%20that%20much%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20is%20based%20on%20tokenism%20like%20creating%20new%20icons%20and%20histories%2C%20making%20positive%20gestures%2C%20and%20empowering%20Adivasi%20individuals%20to%20entice%20Adivasis%20into%20the%20fold%20of%20Hindutva.%20They%20believe%20that%20none%20of%20these%20have%20improved%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20of%20delivering%20constitutional%20promises%20to%20communities.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20tribal%20welfare%20schemes%20remain%20unfulfilled%20despite%20having%20been%20announced%20with%20much%20political%20fanfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20such%20criticisms%20have%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20even%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20have%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20for%20using%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evanvasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(forest-dwellers)%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20reference%20for%20Adivasis%2C%20considered%20derogatory%20by%20many%20in%20the%20community.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20outreach%20has%20focussed%20more%20on%20material%20issues%20like%20implementation%20of%20legal%20safeguards%20for%20communities%20like%20the%20proper%20implementation%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20(PESA)%20Act%2C%201996%20that%20will%20empower%20the%20gram%20sabhas%20to%20take%20policy%20decisions%2C%20or%20implementation%20of%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20(2006)%20that%20recognises%20the%20rights%20of%20Adivasi%20communities%20over%20land%20and%20forest%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoor%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20many%20of%20these%20long-term%20welfare%20of%20Adivasi%20communities%2C%20the%20BJP%20fares%20quite%20poorly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpqars.nic.in%2Fannex%2F257%2FAU459.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20answer%20submitted%20by%20the%20Union%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20July%202022%2C%C2%A0%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20governments%20performed%20the%20worst%20in%20giving%20land%20titles%20to%20Adivasis%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act.%20While%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(77%25)%20and%20Odisha%20(71%25)%20fared%20better%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2050.4%25%20fulfilled%20claims%2C%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20(51%25)%2C%20Assam%20(38%25)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(47%25)%2C%20Uttarakhand%20(3%25)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(46%25)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(20%25)%20performed%20poorly.%20Among%20the%20BJP-led%20states%2C%20only%20Tripura%20with%2064%25%20performed%20better%20than%20the%20national%20average.%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20were%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20until%20last%20year%2C%20had%20an%20abysmal%205%25%20fulfillment%20of%20claims%20until%202022.%C2%A0%20Although%20Congress-led%20states%20like%20Chhattisgarh%20(53%25)%20and%20Rajasthan%20(52%25)%20or%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha-led%20Jharkhand%20(56%25)%20haven%E2%80%99t%20performed%20exceedingly%20well%2C%20their%20performance%20is%20much%20better%20than%20those%20run%20by%20the%20saffron%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F12150321%2FAdivasi_women.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F12150321%2FAdivasi_women.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F12150321%2FAdivasi_women-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F12150321%2FAdivasi_women-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-613438%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdivasi%20women%20in%20Mednipur%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20Photo%3A%20Koustav2007%2FCC%20BY-SA%203.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20of%20implementing%20the%20Tribal%20Sub-Plan%20(TSP)%2C%20which%20mandates%20earmarking%208.2%25%20of%20central%20schemes%20and%20centrally-sponsored%20schemes%20for%20the%20targeted%20welfare%20of%20Adivasis%2C%20is%20abysmal.%20Diversion%20of%20funds%20meant%20for%20the%20TSP%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Sub-Plan%20(SCSP)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20requires%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20earmark%2015.49%25%20of%20all%20central%20schemes%20for%20the%20targeted%20welfare%20of%20Dalits%20%E2%80%93%20have%20reached%20a%20new%20high%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Although%20all%20the%20previous%20governments%20had%20diverted%20funds%20meant%20for%20TSP%20and%20SCSP%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20used%20a%20great%20portion%20of%20these%20funds%20for%20infrastructure%20work%20like%20roads%2C%20flyovers%2C%20buildings%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncdhr.org.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20National%20Campaign%20for%20Dalit%20Human%20Rights%20%E2%80%93%20Dalit%20Arthik%20Adhikar%20Andolan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%20for%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20rights%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20targeted%20budgetary%20allocations%20for%20tribals%20should%20ideally%20be%208.2%25%20of%20the%20allocations%20for%20central%20and%20centrally-sponsored%20schemes%20remained%20between%202.5%25%20in%202018-19%20and%203.6%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20dropping%20even%20lower%20to%201.7%25%20in%202023-24.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20group%20also%20reported%20that%20many%20of%20these%20schemes%20announced%20as%20targeted%20allocations%20for%20adivasis%20are%20used%20for%20the%20general%20welfare%20of%20the%20region%2C%20instead%20of%20specific%20empowerment%20programmes%20for%20Adivasis%20like%20student%20scholarships%2C%20skill%20development%20programmes%2C%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgain%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2FBJP-Poor-Record-Tribal-Welfare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecrimes%20against%20Adivasis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%20are%20on%20the%20rise.%20Reported%20crimes%20against%20Adivasis%20were%206%2C573%20in%202016%2C%207%2C125%20in%202017%2C%206%2C528%20in%202018%2C%208%2C257%20in%202019%2C%20and%208%2C272%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-the-last-75-years-struggles-of-indias-tribal-communities-have-multiplied%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20Last%2075%20Years%2C%20Struggles%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Communities%20Have%20Multiplied%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERanchi-based%20researcher%20and%20activist%20Vasavi%20Kido%2C%20who%20has%20served%20in%20multiple%20governments%20as%20part%20of%20various%20committees%20on%20tribal%20welfare%2C%20said%20that%20although%20there%20has%20been%20a%20flurry%20of%20announcements%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20difference%20in%20adivasi%20lives%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20government%2C%20in%20a%20welcome%20decision%2C%20nominated%20an%20Adviasi%20woman%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20it%20used%20the%20same%20person%20to%20approve%20amendments%20to%20the%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202023%20effectively%20restricts%20the%20scope%20of%20forest%20conservation.%20The%20amendments%20exempted%20multiple%20tracts%20of%20erstwhile%20forest%20lands%20from%20the%20purview%20of%20conservation%20to%20aid%20the%20construction%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20linear%20projects%20of%20national%20importance%20and%20allow%20development%20projects%20like%20running%20zoos%20and%20eco-tourism%20on%20forest%20lands.%20Many%20activists%20believe%20that%20this%20will%20further%20hamper%20adivasis%20who%20depend%20on%20forest%20and%20forest%20resources%2C%20as%20the%20amendments%20will%20allow%20the%20Centre%20to%20take%20control%20over%2C%20say%2C%2040%25%20of%20Aravalli%20range%20and%2095%25%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20hill%20range%20where%20adivasis%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20establishment%20of%20mining%20and%20industrial%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20even%20the%20minimal%20budgetary%20allocations%20meant%20for%20adivasis%20are%20not%20spent.%20Almost%2060%25%20of%20the%20allocations%20remain%20unspent.%20The%20trend%20has%20been%20the%20same%20every%20year.%C2%A0%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20big%20announcements%20do%20not%20matter%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kido%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20tribal%20research%20institutes%20meant%20to%20advance%20Adivasi%20languages%20and%20culture%20continue%20to%20remain%20poorly%20funded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBig%20announcements%2C%20however%2C%20fulfill%20another%20goal%2C%20that%20of%20a%20poll%20promise%20to%20attract%20Adivasis.%20In%20the%20ongoing%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Paricularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%20(PVTG%2C%20formerly%20called%20primitive%20tribal%20group)%20is%20also%20meant%20for%20the%20same%20purpose.%20Modi%20has%20also%20indicated%20that%20a%20bulk%20of%20these%20new%20schemes%20related%20to%20education%2C%20health%2C%20and%20drinking%20water%20will%20be%20funded%20and%20supervised%20by%20the%20World%20Bank.%20It%20remains%20unclear%20whether%20the%20Centre%20will%20have%20any%20accountability%20in%20these%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20these%20election-day%20declarations%2C%20one%20noteworthy%20progress%20has%20been%20made%2C%20according%20to%20Kido.%20The%20Tribal%20Affairs%20ministry%20under%20Arjun%20Munda%20has%20integrated%20ethno-medicine%20of%20Adivasis%20in%20the%20Ayush%20ministry.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20welcome%20step%20as%20this%20would%20help%20popularise%20Adivasi%20medicines%20and%20create%20employment.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20recognition%20of%20PVTG%20as%20a%20group%20that%20needs%20special%20attention%20is%20also%20welcome%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kido.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20often%20noted%20internationally%20for%20malnourishment%20and%20poor%20health%20indicators.%20Which%20are%20these%20areas%2C%20one%20must%20ask.%20These%20are%20regions%20where%20adivasis%20live.%20This%20is%20tribal%20India%20which%20continues%20to%20be%20overlooked%20in%20the%20larger%20development%20goals%20of%20governments.%20We%20need%20to%20do%20much%20more%20than%20merely%20making%20announcements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kido%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700568297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F21172235%2FThe-Wire-83.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffailed-promises-and-tokenism-why-modis-renewed-tribal-push-doesnt-exude-confidence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Prime%20Minister's%20special%20focus%20on%20tribals%20this%20election%20season%20can't%20be%20missed%20given%20that%20they%20constitute%20a%20sizeable%20voting%20bloc%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20states.%20However%2C%20his%20tall%20talk%20on%20tribal%20welfare%20doesn't%20match%20with%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffailed-promises-and-tokenism-why-modis-renewed-tribal-push-doesnt-exude-confidence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eurovision%20winner%20on%20Russia%20wanted%20list%20says%20Kremlin%20is%20trying%20to%20'scare'%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700568120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-susana-jamaladinova_6367483.jpg%3F20231121121739%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjamala-ukrainian-eurovision-winner-on-russia-wanted-list-says-kremlin-is-trying-to-scare-her-13012874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Eurovision%20winner%20who%20has%20been%20added%20to%20Russia's%20wanted%20list%20says%20the%20Kremlin%20is%20lying%20about%20her%20and%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bscare%26quot%3B%20her%20-%20as%20she%20voiced%20fears%20for%20her%20family's%20safety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjamala-ukrainian-eurovision-winner-on-russia-wanted-list-says-kremlin-is-trying-to-scare-her-13012874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjamala-ukrainian-eurovision-winner-